column2: SELECT TOP #  G.ra,G.dec,G.modelMag_r,G.modelMagErr_r,G.extinction_r, pz.z,pz.zErr, G.modelFlux_u, G.modelFlux_g, G.modelFlux_r, G.modelFlux_i, G.modelFlux_z, G.modelFluxIvar_u,G.modelFluxIvar_g,G.modelFluxIvar_r,G.modelFluxIvar_i,G.modelFluxIvar_z,GN.distance FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS GN JOIN Galaxy AS G ON GN.objID = G.objID JOIN PhotoTag AS pt ON pt.objID = G.objID JOIN Photoz AS pz ON GN.objID = pz.objID ORDER by distance
